<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Elisabeth von Kleve, Herzogin von Bayern-Ingolstadt</head><p>Der Rat teilt die Bereitschaft des Judenrates zu Nürnberg zur Ausrichtung des Streits zwischen Feif Groß, Jude zu Nürnberg, und Kalman N., Jude zu Geisenfeld, bis Mariae Lichtmess mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l3">Frawn Elıſabeth pfallncʒgrefin bey Reyn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l4">vnd <expan>hercʒogin<ex>n</ex></expan> in Peyern etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l5">Gnedıge frawe als vns eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>kalman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l6"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> Juden ʒu geyſenueld . vnd des groſſen feıfs Juden bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l7">vns <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l8"><expan>furſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>kalma<ex>n</ex></expan> Jud . ſelb ʒu vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l9">nıht <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> vns mıt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef ein ſchrift getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l10">hat der wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> hıerynn verſloſſen <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l11">Vnd auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſein ſchrıft . darinn er ſıch erpeẅt der ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l12">gen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> feıfs <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> / bey dem Judenrate bey vns ʒu <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l13"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu eren mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> feıfs Juden <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l14">geredt . Daʒ er <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſache bey dem Judenrat bey vns auch <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l17">ſol vnd wıl vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l16">darauf </ab></add> mıt dem Judenrate bey vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l15"><expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab></add> geredt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l18">daʒ ſıe vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ ſıe <expan>ʒwiſche<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Juden auſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l19">ſprechen <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>kalma<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> Jud . das hıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l20"><expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> lıechtmeſſ ſchıerıſt <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vnd begert / Denn wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l21">wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> katherıne </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Elisabeth pfallnczgrefin bey Reyn und
                            <expan>herczogin<ex>n</ex></expan> in Peyern etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige frawe, als uns ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Kalman<ex>n</ex>s</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> juden zu Geysenveld und des Grossen Feifs
                        juden bey uns <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>furstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Kalma<ex>n</ex></expan> jud selb zu uns niht
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> uns
                        mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> brief ein schrift getan hat, der wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> hierynn
                        verslossen <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und auf
                            <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sein schrift, darinn er sich erpewt der
                        sache gen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Feifs
                            <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem judenrate bey uns zu
                                <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu eren mit
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Feifs juden
                            <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> geredt, daz er
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache bey dem judenrat bey uns
                        auch <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan> sol und wil; und
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch <add>darauf</add> mit dem judenrate
                        bey uns <add><expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></add> geredt, daz sie uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> juden auszsprechen
                                <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>Kalma<ex>n</ex></expan>, ewr <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> jud, das
                        hie <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">liechtmess schierist</q>02.02.1421</note>
</app>
<expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> und begert. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Katherine.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
